Fish sampling conducted in 75 m stretch before culvert downstream as well as 50 m stretch up chain of colour with Fish tagged were above 60 mm.   There are baffles made of metal within the culvert and the 3/4 of the upstream of the pipe is embedded with some material. The outlet of the pipe sits on a large roll of rip rock so that is about a 30 cm cascade that occurs approximately metre after The outlet of the pipe.          ,,2024-09-11T22:58:48Z,10,534595,6067775,No,,,No,,0.5,0.23,0.15,No,2,5,1.5,Yes,Yes,Deep Fill,High,,,,,,,,,,,,newgraph_airvine,No,Yes,,high,2,1,1,4,Covert is in decent shape besides the fact that it has down cut at the outlet. ",1,1,7,5,10,8,32,40,"This is a 4 Service Rd. that accesses areas used for forestry as well as the CN rail line. No communities or residential houses upstream.
